---
description: "Flutter localization guardrails"
globs:
  - "app/**/*.dart"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use l10n for all user-facing strings: `context.l10n.keyName`.
- Add ARB keys with `jq`; avoid loading entire ARB files.
- Translate all 33 non-English locales; keep placeholders identical.
- Regenerate l10n after ARB edits: `cd app && flutter gen-l10n`.
- See AGENTS.md for full rules.
